<title>CHINA: China reiterates ban on loans for stock trading.</title>
<headline>China reiterates ban on loans for stock trading.</headline>
<dateline>SHANGHAI 1996-10-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>The China Securities Regulatory Commission has reaffirmed its ban on stock trading on credit, the China Securities Newspaper said on Tuesday.</p>
<p>The newspaper said the regulator had discovered that some securities companies were still providing credit for their clients for stock trading, which is banned.</p>
<p>It gave no details.</p>
</text>
